  "texts": [
    "They enable proactive security measures and minimize the risk of unauthorized access.",
    "AI and ML can help with the continuous and automatic discovery of all devices, applications and users, as well as their classification and criticality for operations.",
    "With an accurate and upto-date inventory, assets can be tracked and analyzed for a risk assessment against known attack vectors, and compliance monitors can detect rogue assets and unauthorized use.",
    "• Business environment -The business environment category plays a crucial role in identifying essential processes and applications that are essential for maintaining business continuity during challenging situations.",
    "This knowledge is vital for the long-term viability of a business and serves as the foundation for establishing robust response and recovery strategies."
  ]
